s/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3776:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5705 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/seohub.jpg" alt="SEOHub SEO、营销类wordpress主题" width="590" height="300" /></p>\n<p>SEOHub是一套适合SEO、营销推广类网站使用的<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/" title="wordpress主题" target="_blank">wordpress主题</a></span>。这套主题设计时尚现代，采用响应式布局，优化了手机端的访问体验，内置兼容多个强大的插件，例如Visual Composer、WPML、WooCommerce、Revolution Slider等，并且通过配合Visual Composer插件及短代码功能可以制作出各种布局元素的页面。SEOHub还支持页面滚动的动画效果，演示数据也可以通过后台直接一键导入。</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5706 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/SEOHub-desc.jpg" alt="SEOHub SEO、营销类wordpress主题" width="616" height="3569" /></p>\n<h3 id="item-description__key-features">主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Simple and Functional design</li>\n<li>Easy to install, run and update!</li>\n<li>Modern, Flexible, Customizable!</li>\n<li>WordPress 4.0+ Tested and Approved!</li>\n<li>Built with valid HTML5 and CSS3 code</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE9+</li>\n<li>One-Click demo install</li>\n<li><strong>Layout Features</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Boxed and Wide pages layouts</li>\n<li>Visual Composer support – create unlimited variants of Homepage Layouts</li>\n<li>Different Header Styles</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Multi-Functional User Panel</li>\n<li>Many awesome Hover Effects</li>\n<li>Fully Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Retina Option</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Slider Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Includes Swiper Slider for posts and galleries</li>\n<li>Includes Revolution Slider as Home slider</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Navigation Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>User menu and Main menu support</li>\n<li>Main menu slider</li>\n<li>Awesome CSS3/jQuery animation effects</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Powerful Framework</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Setting Inheritance and Override System</li>\n<li>Shortcode Builder</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n<li>Custom Theme Options Panel</li>\n<li>Media Content Manager</li>\n<li>Optimized for best performance</li>\n<li>&#8230;and many more!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Plugins Compatibility</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Sliders: Swiper Slider, Revolution Slider</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n<li>Essential Grid</li>\n<li>PO Composer!</li>\n<li>WooCommerce</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Custom Widgets Set</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Flickr</li>\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Instagram</li>\n<li>Popular Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Reviews</li>\n<li>Top 10</li>\n<li>Advertisment</li>\n<li>Logo</li>\n<li>Social Icons</li>\n<li>King Size Shortcodes Pack</li>\n<li>Blogger</li>\n<li>Content Slider</li>\n<li>Skills</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Custom Shortcodes</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Blogger</li>\n<li>Lense</li>\n<li>Content Slider</li>\n<li>Video List</li>\n<li>Skills</li>\n<li>eMailer</li>\n<li>Timeline</li>\n<li>Scroller</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>A lot of <strong>Shortcodes</strong> included:\n<ul>\n<li>Accordion</li>\n<li>Button</li>\n<li>Columns</li>\n<li>Google Map</li>\n<li>Hide</li>\n<li>Highlight</li>\n<li>Section</li>\n<li>Table</li>\n<li>Tabs</li>\n<li>Team</li>\n<li>Testimonials</li>\n<li>Title</li>\n<li>Tooltip</li>\n<li>Toggle</li>\n<li>and more …</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Interactive Ajax Search mechanism</li>\n<li>Two variants of icon display: Fontella Icon set and Images Icons</li>\n<li>Google web fonts</li>\n<li>Performance Optimization</li>\n<li>Great Professional Support</li>\n<li>Documentation included</li>\n<li>Regular Updates</li>\n<li>And many more that we might have forgotten to mention…</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/seohub.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"