s/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1999:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5673 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/GridStack.png" alt="GridStack 简洁的wordpress企业主题" width="590" height="300" /></p>\n<p>GridStack是来自<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>的一套非常简洁清爽的<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/" title="wordpress主题" target="_blank">wordpress主题</a></span>，在<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>网站的销量是非常不错的。GridStack主题如她的名字一般，最大的亮点就是格子图片布局，并且支持筛选功能以及无刷新Ajax加载功能。GridStack还支持多种页面布局风格模版，后台可以自定义颜色，并且支持响应式，兼容移动设备。</p>\n<h3>更多特色</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>WPML Multi-Language Certified Compatible!</li>\n<li>Responsive Design: Tablet and Mobile Optimized</li>\n<li>SEO-Friendly, Ajaxified Navigation for a Smoother UI</li>\n<li>Unique Slideshow and Gallery Options</li>\n<li>Themewich Shortcodes Plugin Included</li>\n<li>Feature blog posts and portfolio items</li>\n<li>Sortable Portfolio</li>\n<li>Unlimited Colors</li>\n<li>Multiple Blog Styles</li>\n<li>500+ Google Fonts</li>\n<li>XML and SQL files included to load default content.</li>\n<li>Touch/Swipe Support for Sliders</li>\n<li>4 Custom WordPress Widgets</li>\n<li>Powerfully Simple Theme Options</li>\n<li>Working Contact Form – right out of the box</li>\n<li>Extensive Documentation and Dedicated Support Forum</li>\n<li>Child Theme Support for Advanced Users</li>\n<li>Translation-Ready .po/.mo files inlcuded</li>\n<li>Much More! Check out the live preview!</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a