an class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>的单页面<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/" title="wordpress主题" target="_blank">wordpress主题</a></span>，AppStack主题的设计风格也非常时尚大方，功能方面也是比较多的，幻灯片、视频、tab、响应式、WPML多语言、动画效果以及自定义等等，作为一套单页面主题，它还是很适合用于APP应用程序等产品的介绍展示。</p>\n<h3 id="item-description__features-list">主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Fully Responsive</li>\n<li>Page Builder</li>\n<li>Custom Headers</li>\n<li>Customizable Page Templates</li>\n<li>Color Customizer</li>\n<li>Animated Points of Interest</li>\n<li>Custom Animated Modals</li>\n<li>Animated Device Switcher</li>\n<li>Animated Video Modal</li>\n<li>Contact Form7 Integration</li>\n<li>FontAwesome Icons</li>\n<li>Advanced Custom Fields Pro</li>\n<li>RTL Support</li>\n<li>WPML Support</li>\n<li>Demo Content</li>\n<li>Great Support</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/appstack.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:11;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:54:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:42:"Classter 时尚大气wordpress企业主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:40:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/classter.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/classter.html#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 03 Mar 2016 12:38:54 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"高级主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"themeforest";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:21:"wordpress企业主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:21:"wordpress商城主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"自定义";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"http://www.iztwp.com/premium/.html";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:411:"Classter 是来自themeforest的一套wordpress企业主题，这套主题非常时尚大气高端，功能也非常强大，从菜单、幻灯片、商城、特效到后台自定义、短代码等等，一应俱全。Classter还支持多种页面模板布局选择，例如首页、头部、尾部、博客等都有多种可以选择。 主题特色 Modern, Flexible, Multi-purpose! WordPress 4.1+ Tested an...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"爱主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4724:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5644 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Classter.jpg" alt="Classter 时尚大气wordpress企业主题" width="590" height="300" /></p>\n<p>Classter 是来自<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>的一套<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/tag/business-theme" title="wordpress企业主题" target="_blank">wordpress企业主题</a></span>，这套主题非常时尚大气高端，功能也非常强大，从菜单、幻灯片、商城、特效到后台自定义、短代码等等，一应俱全。Classter还支持多种页面模板布局选择，例如首页、头部、尾部、博客等都有多种可以选择。</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5645" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Classter_dscr.png" alt="Classter 时尚大气wordpress企业主题" width="616" height="7876" /></p>\n<h3 id="item-description__key-features">主题特色</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Modern, Flexible, Multi-purpose!</li>\n<li>WordPress 4.1+ Tested and Approved!</li>\n<li>Built with HTML5 and CSS3</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE9+</li>\n<li>One-Click demo install</li>\n<li>Child theme support</li>\n<li><strong>Layout Features</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>10 Homepage Layouts</li>\n<li>5 Header Styles</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Multi-Functional User Panel</li>\n<li>2 Footer Styles</li>\n<li>4 Slider Styles</li>\n<li>9 Blog Styles, including unique Tab Style from ThemeRex!</li>\n<li>9 variants for 3 Portfolio Styles: Classic, Masonry &amp; Grid</li>\n<li>2 styles for Portfolio Post</li>\n<li>Fully Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Retina Option</li>\n<li>Parallax and Video Background</li>\n<li>Advanced User login panel</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Slider Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Includes Swiper Slider</li>\n<li>Includes Revolution Slider</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Framework</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Unique Setting Inheritance and Override System</li>\n<li>Shortcode Builder</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n<li>Custom Theme Options Panel</li>\n<li>Media Content Manager</li>\n<li>&#8230;and many more!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Raiting\\Review Mechanism</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Assign a set of rating criteria for each category</li>\n<li>Add author’s and users’ rating both simultaneously and individually</li>\n<li>Choose one of the three rating styles: five stars, 10 grades, or 100 %</li>\n<li>Assign level of permit for visitors to rate your review</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Translation Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Localized: .po &amp; .mo files included</li>\n<li>PO Composer: working with .po and .mo files has now become much easier!</li>\n<li>WPML plugin compatible</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Plugins Compatibility</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Sliders: Swiper Slider, Royal Slider, FlexSlider, Revolution Slider</li>\n<li>WPML plugin</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n<li>WooCommerce</li>\n<li>BuddyPress &amp; bbPress</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Widgets Set</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Flickr</li>\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Instagramm</li>\n<li>Popular Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Reviews</li>\n<li>Top 10</li>\n<li>Advertisement</li>\n<li>Logo</li>\n<li>Social Icons</li>\n<li>QR-cod</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Unique <strong>ThemeRex Shortcodes</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Blogger</li>\n<li>Lense</li>\n<li>Content Slider</li>\n<li>Skills</li>\n<li>eMailer</li>\n<li>Timeline</li>\n<li>Scroller</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>A lot of <strong>Shortcodes</strong> included: Accordion, Blogger, Button, Columns, Google Map, Hide, Highlight, Table, Team, Title, Tooltip, Section, Skills, Tabs, Testimonial, Toggle, and more …</li>\n<li><strong>WooCommerce</strong> ready with full design integration</li>\n<li><strong>Interactive Ajax Search mechanism</strong></li>\n<li><strong>SEO Ready</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>HTML code integrated into the theme meets the best SEO approaches</li>\n<li>The theme support compatibility with “All on One SEO Pack” &amp; “SEO by Yoast”</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Save money with <strong>Included Plugins</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Revolution Slider – $19</li>\n<li>Visual Composer – $30</li>\n<li>PO Composer – $16</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Performance Optimization</li>\n<li>Two variants of icon display: Fontella Icon set and Images Icons</li>\n<li>Google web fonts</li>\n<li>Great Professional Support</li>\n<li>Documentation included</li>\n<li>Regular Updates</li>\n<li>And many more that we might have forgotten to mention…</li>\n</ul>\n<p>All images/illustrations are for preview purposes only and are not included in the download files.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/classter.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:12;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:37:"Codeus WordPress响应式企业主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:38:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/codeus.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:46:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/codeus.html#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Fri, 19 Feb 2016 07:34:21 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"高级主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"themeforest";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Woocommerce";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:21:"wordpress企业主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"WPML";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"响应式";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"http://www.iztwp.com/premium/.html";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:395:"Codeus是来自themeforest的一套wordpress企业主题，这套主题设计非常美观现代清爽，支持响应式布局，能够在移动设备上访问。在功能方面，主题支持WooCommerce插件实现商城功能，WPML插件实现多语言功能，支持页面生产插件实现页面布局自定义。 主题介绍 General: Awesome design built in collaboration with award-win...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"爱主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7256:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5638 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Codeus.jpg" alt="Codeus WordPress响应式企业主题" width="590" height="300" /></p>\n<p>Codeus是来自<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>的一套<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/tag/business-theme" title="wordpress企业主题" target="_blank">wordpress企业主题</a></span>，这套主题设计非常美观现代清爽，支持响应式布局，能够在移动设备上访问。在功能方面，主题支持WooCommerce插件实现商城功能，WPML插件实现多语言功能，支持页面生产插件实现页面布局自定义。</p>\n<h3>主题介绍</h3>\n<p><strong>General:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Awesome design built in collaboration with award-winning designer Kontramax</li>\n<li>Fresh modern flat look combined with strict content presentation for business or portfolio website</li>\n<li>Ready-to-use as well as full customizable</li>\n<li>Detailed documentation, icons, fancy backgrounds, psds and demo content are included</li>\n<li>Premium powerful LayerSlider for building spectacular slideshows included</li>\n<li>Built in styles for the free Contact Form 7 plugin</li>\n<li>Free support</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Ready-To-Use Skins:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose from two awesome pre-configured skins: light &amp; dark</li>\n<li>Easy-to-change skin styles</li>\n<li>Backup &amp; restore skin settings</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Powerful Admin Panel &amp; Style Manager:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Customize just anything in an appearance of your website with few clicks</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Unlimited Colors &amp; Custom Backgrounds:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Customizable backgrounds for headers, sliders, slideshow area, quickfinder, main content, contact panels etc.</li>\n<li>You can use colors or images / patterns to customize your backgrounds</li>\n<li>Fancy header background patterns are included</li>\n<li>Extensive color customization settings in admin panel</li>\n<li>Customizable colors in almost any page elements</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Awesome Customizable Typography:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>300+ google fonts and websafe fonts</li>\n<li>Font Manager to easily include and use your own webfonts</li>\n<li>upload your own google fonts &amp; webfont files</li>\n<li>easy-to-use settings for sizes, colors, line heights for any content element</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Homepage Constructor:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Easily build your own unique hompage using drag&amp;drop</li>\n<li>Use and combine any post types with any content</li>\n<li>Organize your homepage in just 1 min!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Extensive Portfolios:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Multiple flexible portfolio layouts</li>\n<li>Grid, slider &amp; list overviews</li>\n<li>Filterable with spectacular filtering effects</li>\n<li>Portfolios in page settings</li>\n<li>Portfolios as shortcode</li>\n<li>Multiple types of portfolio items</li>\n<li>Portfolio pages, video &amp; image lightboxes, external &amp; internal pages</li>\n<li>Full-Width, half-width, sidebar portfolio pages</li>\n<li>Sortable &amp; filterable portfolio sets/ categories</li>\n<li>Awesome portfolio info custom widget</li>\n<li>Tons of easy-to-use portfolio settings</li>\n<li>Automatic pagination</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Amazing Galleries:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose from 4 gallery layouts &amp; 6 different gallery styles</li>\n<li>Medium thumbs grid, small thumbs grid, slider full-width, slider half-width</li>\n<li>Business galleries with bottom sliders</li>\n<li>Simple gallery settings inside the page options</li>\n<li>Flexible gallery integration on any position</li>\n<li>Gallery shortcode</li>\n<li>Lightboxes with image captions</li>\n<li>Full customizable gallery styles (colors, backgrounds, fonts)</li>\n<li>Uploader supports multiple images upload</li>\n<li>Easy organize galleries with drag&amp;drop</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Useful Quickfinders:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Help user to navigate on website</li>\n<li>Highlight special USPs of your products/services</li>\n<li>Use any images or modern flat icons with trendy shadows for building your quickfinders</li>\n<li>200+ Font Icons included</li>\n<li>Icons are fully customizable in appearance</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Spectacular Slideshows:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Header slideshows</li>\n<li>Product presentations &amp; showcases</li>\n<li>Powerful premium LayerSlider plugin included</li>\n<li>Nivo slider with tons of beautiful transition effects</li>\n<li>Easily managed in admin panel</li>\n<li>Use slideshows on any page you wish: both as page settings or shortcodes</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Clients presentation:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Present your customers in awesome grids or attractive sliders</li>\n<li>Both as page settings or as shortcodes</li>\n<li>Filterable with spectacular filtering effects</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Flexible Page Options: </strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fully customizable pages</li>\n<li>Built-in numerous page settings for:</li>\n<li>Custom fancy page header</li>\n<li>Lazy loading page animations</li>\n<li>Slideshows</li>\n<li>Quickfinders</li>\n<li>Portfolios</li>\n<li>Galleries</li>\n<li>Clients</li>\n<li>Sidebars</li>\n<li>Shortcode generator</li>\n<li>Full-width, left /right sidebar</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Powerful and Easy-to-use Visual Composer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Frontend Editor For Real WYSIWYG Experience</li>\n<li>Powerful Backend Editor To Build Any Layouts</li>\n<li>All Codeus Shortcodes are included</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Shortcode Generator With Tons of Shortcodes:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Built-in easy-to-use shortcode generator in pages, portfolios, blog posts etc.</li>\n<li>Tons of shortcodes for any needs: Galleries, Portfolios, Quickfinders, Clients, Slideshows, Diagrams, Pricing Tables, Teams, Feedback Forms, Font Icons, Styled Boxes, Styled Images, Tabs, Accordions, Maps, Videos, Divider, Tables, Typography, Buttons, Column Layouts and much more!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Unlimited Full-Customizable Sidebars:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Equip pages with individual sidebars</li>\n<li>Create own sidebar for any page</li>\n<li>Use default sidebars for pages with the same sidebar content</li>\n<li>Left or right sidebars</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Built-in Custom Widgets:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>WYSIWYG / Richt Text Widget</li>\n<li>Project Info / Contact Info / Custom iconed fields</li>\n<li>Picturebox Widget</li>\n<li>Interactive Diagrams</li>\n<li>Text/Infobox Widget (with shortcode support)</li>\n<li>Submenu / Side Sub-Navigation Widget</li>\n<li>Team Widget</li>\n<li>Testimonials Widget</li>\n<li>Twitter Widget</li>\n<li>Flickr / Photostream Widget</li>\n<li>Facebook Widget</li>\n<li>Recent / Popular Posts</li>\n<li>Custom Menu Widget</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>WooCommerce Compatibility :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Codeus is WooCommerce ready</li>\n<li>Design integration of all online shop templates</li>\n<li>Full width &amp; sidebar shop page</li>\n<li>Responsive &amp; SEO ready</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Wide &amp; Boxed Layouts:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Customizable backround color for boxed layout</li>\n<li>Customizable background images / patterns for boxed layout</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:43:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/codeus.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:13;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:39:"Symetrio 运动健身类WordPress主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:40:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/symetrio.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/symetrio.html#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 03 Feb 2016 05:21:09 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"高级主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"bbpress";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"themeforest";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"Woocommerce";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:21:"wordpress企业主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"运动健身";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"http://www.iztwp.com/premium/.html";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:409:"Symetrio是一套来自themeforest的运动健身类wordpress企业主题。这套主题非常简洁大方，在themeforest网站运动健身同类主题里面销量第一。Symetrio 支持多种首页风格，具体每种风格的效果可以查看演示链接。Symetrio 主题还可以配合WooCommerce插件实现商城功能，配合bbPress支持社区交流功能。 主题介绍 Powerfull Schedule m...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"爱主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8553:"<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5633" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Symetrio.png" alt="Symetrio 运动健身类Wordpress主题" width="590" height="303" /></p>\n<p>Symetrio是一套来自<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>的运动健身类<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/tag/business-theme" title="wordpress企业主题" target="_blank">wordpress企业主题</a></span>。这套主题非常简洁大方，在<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>网站运动健身同类主题里面销量第一。Symetrio 支持多种首页风格，具体每种风格的效果可以查看演示链接。Symetrio 主题还可以配合WooCommerce插件实现商城功能，配合bbPress支持社区交流功能。</p>\n<h3>主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Powerfull Schedule module – create simple module and advanced schedules. Use prdefined modules</li>\n<li>Multi place location – Symetrio supports multiple clubs locations. You can narrow trainers set / activities / rooms form by assigning them a specific location</li>\n<li>Event module</li>\n<li>One Page template</li>\n<li>PayPal payment integration</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE9, IE10, IE11</li>\n<li>Sticky header – You can decide about header menu visibility</li>\n<li>Smart – Menu</li>\n<li>Full width &amp; Boxed mode</li>\n<li>Fancy mobile menu</li>\n<li>Standard &amp; Mega Menu</li>\n<li>Paralax Background</li>\n<li>2 totaly different blog styles</li>\n<li>Video Background (You can use a local video / stream from YouTube or Vimeo)</li>\n<li>Free &amp; outstanding support for customers\n<ul>\n<li>Full Online Documentation</li>\n<li>FREE Lifetime Updates – get all the new features we add in each future update for free</li>\n<li>We take pride in offering THE BEST after sales support around. We care about your site as much as you do, and we will help in any possible way</li>\n<li>Multiple HD video tutorials for easy instruction</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><b>Included 40 CSS3 animations</b></li>\n<li>Awesome Wonster Slider</li>\n<li>Instagram Integration</li>\n<li>Mega backgorund – animated background ( from selected photos ) on your page.</li>\n<li>WordPress Multi-Site (WPMU) – Tested and Approved</li>\n<li><b>Unlimited colors element – Change theme colors using built-in WordPress Customization panel</b></li>\n<li>Social media integration</li>\n<li>Amazing Google Maps Builder\n<ul>\n<li>The mechanism for creating paths and tracks</li>\n<li>Street view</li>\n<li>Unlimited number of pins on your map</li>\n<li>Your own, custom map pin</li>\n<li>70 predefined map styles</li>\n<li>100 predefined map pins</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>3 Different Blog Layouts</li>\n<li>4 Headers, 6 Fotters</li>\n<li>Build your site in a simple way. Build your site in a simple way. You get probably the best shortcode mechanism throughout the whole Evanto. Create unlimited layouts, chose from over 60 difrent type of shortcodes. Create layouts with no limitations.\n<ul>\n<li>48 functional shortcodes</li>\n<li>12 fitness – shortcodes\n<ul>\n<li>Class – allows you to display specific classes, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Classes – allows you to crate lists with classes, available filtering after, category and  gym location, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Class schedule – wit static / multi week module</li>\n<li>Daily schedule – classes for specific day in condensed form</li>\n<li>Event – allows you to display specific event</li>\n<li>Events – allows you to crate lists with events, available filtering after, category and  gym location, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Open hours – dedicated element allows you to display open hours in your club</li>\n<li>Pass –  dedicated element allows you to display specific club pass</li>\n<li>Passes – allows you to crate lists with passes, available filtering after, category and  gym location</li>\n<li>Rooms – allows you to crate lists with rooms, available filtering after, category and  gym location</li>\n<li>Trainer – allows you to display specific trainer, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n<li>Trainers – allows you to crate lists with trainers, available filtering after, category, gym location, specializations, trainers functions, available 2 forms of presentation</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Amazing Wonster Options\n<ul>\n<li>Change color for each element you see</li>\n<li>Turn on/off responsive version by one click</li>\n<li>Turn on/off Boxed style</li>\n<li>Change phone &amp; email in header withing seconds</li>\n<li>Choose between different layouts with one click</li>\n<li>Use built-in SEO fields</li>\n<li>Unlimited sidebars</li>\n<li>Choose fonts for each text on page (you can use Latin, Cyrilic and many other types of font)</li>\n<li>Built-in translator (translate anything you want on page with our built-in translator)</li>\n<li>Choose between backgrounds images, colors, etc.</li>\n<li>Upload logo &amp; favicon in few seconds</li>\n<li>Retina Ready</li>\n<li>Blog options support</li>\n<li>Portfolio options support</li>\n<li>Custom CSS support</li>\n<li>and much more</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>New Page Options – For each side there is a number of interesting options to help you affect appearance of the page\n<ul>\n<li>Page menu – allows you to set a different menu on each page</li>\n<li>Enable clean menu mode</li>\n<li>Enable transparent mode</li>\n<li>Show/hide breadcumbs</li>\n<li>Sidebar position – Decide about the visibility of the sidebar and its position. For each page, you can assign different sidebar.</li>\n<li>Custom css – You can make quick modifications to the appearance of each page by adding your own CSS code.</li>\n<li>Header settings</li>\n<li>Footer Settings</li>\n<li>SEO – manage seo fields for each page.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Advanced Blog Options\n<ul>\n<li>Number of posts per page</li>\n<li>Post excerpt length ( signs )</li>\n<li>Blog style</li>\n<li>Default blog date format</li>\n<li>Show meta</li>\n<li>Show categories</li>\n<li>Show tags</li>\n<li>Social media toolbar</li>\n<li>Show author bio</li>\n<li>Related posts</li>\n<li>Related posts by: Tags / Category / Category &amp; Tags</li>\n<li>Related posts order by: Random / Lastest</li>\n<li>Breadcrumbs container: On / Off</li>\n<li>Breadcrumbs: On / Off</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Advanced Typography Options\n<ul>\n<li>Use 600+ Google Fonts thar are included or Standard Fonts</li>\n<li>All font options are controlled in the theme options panel</li>\n<li>Set different font sizes for all fonts, H1-H6 headings, body, footer, sidebar, etc</li>\n<li>Set different colors for all fonts, H1-H6 headings, body, footer, sidebar, etc</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Custom 404 – Use the default 404 page or build your own unique version of 404</li>\n<li>100% Responsive Theme – and you can easily turn it on or off</li>\n<li>SEO ready\n<ul>\n<li>Built-in SEO fields (use them or turn them off)</li>\n<li>Compatible with plugins like All in One SEO or Yoast</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Super Easy Installation &amp; Setup\n<ul>\n<li>One Click install</li>\n<li>XML file with 3 demo content</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Child Theme Compatible – includes basic child theme!</li>\n<li>Advanced Header Optrions</li>\n<li>Advanced footer Optrions</li>\n<li>Advanced Breadcrumbs Options</li>\n<li>Custom Styles</li>\n<li>Unlimited Sidebars\n<ul>\n<li>Create and manage unlimited unique sidebars</li>\n<li>Set sidebars on either side of the page (left or right)</li>\n<li>Manage all unique sidebars from one interface</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Amazing Revolution Slider – included</li>\n<li>Visual Composer: Page Builder for WordPress – included</li>\n<li>Strong focus on typography, usability and overall user-experience</li>\n<li>Translation Support – translate your website files using PO / MO</li>\n<li>Includes the Font Awesome icon set, fully integrated</li>\n<li>Compatible with Many Popular Plugins</li>\n<li>Unlimited sidebars for pages</li>\n<li>SEO Base Built-In</li>\n<li><b>WPML ready – for all those who need multilingual webs</b>\n<ul>\n<li>Password protected posts in Blog, Photo Albums, Portfolio, Media</li>\n<li>Social media iconst</li>\n<li>Built with HTML5 and CSS3</li>\n<li>Cool jQuery Enhancements</li>\n<li>Fitness Widget</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:45:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/symetrio.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:14;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:57:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:35:"SAHARAN WordPress外贸电商主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:39:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/saharan.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:47:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/saharan.html#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 30 Dec 2015 09:58:56 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"高级主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"themeforest";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"WPML";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"响应式";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"外贸主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"电商主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"http://www.iztwp.com/premium/.html";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:401:"SAHARAN是来自themeforest上面的一套非常强大的wordpress电商主题，SAHARAN的自定义功能非常强大，支持多种页面风格布局（多达46+），可以制作出适用于各个行业的电商网站。SAHARAN主题支持响应式，兼容移动端访问，同时支持WPML插件，可以实现多语言功能。 主题介绍 WordPress 4+ Ready WooCommerce 2.4 Ready WPML suppo...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"爱主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1765:"<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5625" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/SAHARAN.jpg" alt="SAHARAN WordPress外贸电商主题" width="590" height="300" /></p>\n<p>SAHARAN是来自<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>上面的一套非常强大的wordpress电商主题，SAHARAN的自定义功能非常强大，支持多种页面风格布局（多达46+），可以制作出适用于各个行业的电商网站。SAHARAN主题支持响应式，兼容移动端访问，同时支持WPML插件，可以实现多语言功能。</p>\n<h3 id="item-description__overview">主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>WordPress 4+ Ready</li>\n<li>WooCommerce 2.4 Ready</li>\n<li>WPML supported</li>\n<li>Fully Responsive, your website will works on almost device</li>\n<li>Powered by Redux framework, bring to you unlimited color and Google fonts options</li>\n<li>Wishlists, Ajax shopping cart, Product Quick View</li>\n<li>Products carousel, testimonials carousel, latest posts carousel</li>\n<li>Product images zoom for details page</li>\n<li>Grid view and list view for shop page</li>\n<li>39+ home page layouts</li>\n<li>Multiple blog layouts for your choice</li>\n<li>Box layout and full width layout</li>\n<li>Sample background images</li>\n<li>Color presets included</li>\n<li>5 header layouts</li>\n<li>Suitable for the fashion, furniture, digital, accessories, food, cafe, sport shop</li>\n<li>Social icon links</li>\n<li>Error 404 page included</li>\n<li>Multi home page layouts</li>\n<li>Well documented</li>\n<li>Samle content available to help you build your website with demo content</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:44:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/saharan.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:15;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:59:"wordpress 4.4禁用embeds功能 移除wp-embed.min.js文件";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"http://www.iztwp.com/article/disable-embeds.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"http://www.iztwp.com/article/disable-embeds.html#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Mon, 14 Dec 2015 15:07:06 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"WordPress教程";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"oEmbed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Wordpress 4.4";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"http://www.iztwp.com/premium/.html";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:451:"WordPress 4.4新增了不少功能，之前也介绍过禁用REST API的方法，现在再来介绍一下禁用embeds的方法，也就是移除页面输出的wp-embed.min.js文件。wordpress 4.4的embeds功能可以允许更方便的引用第三方资源，具体可以搜下oEmbed，这里不细说了。 禁用embeds其实还是比较复杂（代码比较多），官方甚至为此开发了一个插件，大家可以使用插件来禁用：Di...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"爱主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3600:"<p>WordPress 4.4新增了不少功能，之前也介绍过<a href="http://www.iztwp.com/article/remove-wp-json.html" target="_blank">禁用REST API</a>的方法，现在再来介绍一下禁用embeds的方法，也就是移除页面输出的wp-embed.min.js文件。wordpress 4.4的embeds功能可以允许更方便的引用第三方资源，具体可以搜下oEmbed，这里不细说了。</p>\n<p>禁用embeds其实还是比较复杂（代码比较多），官方甚至为此开发了一个插件，大家可以使用插件来禁用：<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/disable-embeds/" target="_blank">Disable Embeds</a>，如果不想使用插件，那就将插件里面的代码复制到主题的functions.php文件即可。</p>\n<p>代码如下：</p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">function disable_embeds_init() {\r\n    /* @var WP $wp */\r\n    global $wp;\r\n\r\n    // Remove the embed query var.\r\n    $wp-&gt;public_query_vars = array_diff( $wp-&gt;public_query_vars, array(\r\n        ''embed'',\r\n    ) );\r\n\r\n    // Remove the REST API endpoint.\r\n    remove_action( ''rest_api_init'', ''wp_oembed_register_route'' );\r\n\r\n    // Turn off\r\n    add_filter( ''embed_oembed_discover'', ''__return_false'' );\r\n\r\n    // Don''t filter oEmbed results.\r\n    remove_filter( ''oembed_dataparse'', ''wp_filter_oembed_result'', 10 );\r\n\r\n    // Remove oEmbed discovery links.\r\n    remove_action( ''wp_head'', ''wp_oembed_add_discovery_links'' );\r\n\r\n    // Remove oEmbed-specific JavaScript from the front-end and back-end.\r\n    remove_action( ''wp_head'', ''wp_oembed_add_host_js'' );\r\n    add_filter( ''tiny_mce_plugins'', ''disable_embeds_tiny_mce_plugin'' );\r\n\r\n    // Remove all embeds rewrite rules.\r\n    add_filter( ''rewrite_rules_array'', ''disable_embeds_rewrites'' );\r\n}\r\n\r\nadd_action( ''init'', ''disable_embeds_init'', 9999 );\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Removes the ''wpembed'' TinyMCE plugin.\r\n *\r\n * @since 1.0.0\r\n *\r\n * @param array $plugins List of TinyMCE plugins.\r\n * @return array The modified list.\r\n */\r\nfunction disable_embeds_tiny_mce_plugin( $plugins ) {\r\n    return array_diff( $plugins, array( ''wpembed'' ) );\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Remove all rewrite rules related to embeds.\r\n *\r\n * @since 1.2.0\r\n *\r\n * @param array $rules WordPress rewrite rules.\r\n * @return array Rewrite rules without embeds rules.\r\n */\r\nfunction disable_embeds_rewrites( $rules ) {\r\n    foreach ( $rules as $rule =&gt; $rewrite ) {\r\n        if ( false !== strpos( $rewrite, ''embed=true'' ) ) {\r\n            unset( $rules[ $rule ] );\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    return $rules;\r\n}\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Remove embeds rewrite rules on plugin activation.\r\n *\r\n * @since 1.2.0\r\n */\r\nfunction disable_embeds_remove_rewrite_rules() {\r\n    add_filter( ''rewrite_rules_array'', ''disable_embeds_rewrites'' );\r\n    flush_rewrite_rules();\r\n}\r\n\r\nregister_activation_hook( __FILE__, ''disable_embeds_remove_rewrite_rules'' );\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * Flush rewrite rules on plugin deactivation.\r\n *\r\n * @since 1.2.0\r\n */\r\nfunction disable_embeds_flush_rewrite_rules() {\r\n    remove_filter( ''rewrite_rules_array'', ''disable_embeds_rewrites'' );\r\n    flush_rewrite_rules();\r\n}\r\n\r\nregister_deactivation_hook( __FILE__, ''disable_embeds_flush_rewrite_rules'' );</pre><p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>这里不得不吐槽下wordpress，如果每次升级都增加一些功能，并且要在页面输出内容，那必然会影响网站的打开速度，更坑的是如果禁用需要安装插件，那么每次升级都要安装几个插件？</p>\n<p>在wordpress的功能介绍文章下面也有不少用户提出这个问题，有兴趣的童鞋可以去看下：https://make.wordpress.org/core/2015/10/28/new-embeds-feature-in-wordpress-4-4/</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"http://www.iztwp.com/article/disable-embeds.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2:"16";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:16;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:51:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"wordpress 4.4 禁用REST API/移除wp-json链接的方法";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"http://www.iztwp.com/article/remove-wp-json.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"http://www.iztwp.com/article/remove-wp-json.html#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 10 Dec 2015 05:55:41 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"WordPress教程";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"REST API";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Wordpress 4.4";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"wp-json";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"http://www.iztwp.com/premium/.html";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:397:"WordPress 4.4更新新增了REST API功能，通过REST API可以很轻松的获取网站的数据，但是这个功能并不是每个网站都需要的，或者说我需要，但是并不希望他在head里面输出，所以给大家介绍下禁用REST API或者说移除head里面wp-json链接的方法。 禁用REST API [crayon-57d3af2619b2f447443361/] 将以上代码添加到主题function...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"爱主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:732:"<p>WordPress 4.4更新新增了REST API功能，通过REST API可以很轻松的获取网站的数据，但是这个功能并不是每个网站都需要的，或者说我需要，但是并不希望他在head里面输出，所以给大家介绍下禁用REST API或者说移除head里面wp-json链接的方法。</p>\n<h3>禁用REST API</h3>\n<p></p><pre class="crayon-plain-tag">add_filter(''rest_enabled'', ''__return_false'');\r\nadd_filter(''rest_jsonp_enabled'', ''__return_false'');\r\n\r\nremove_action( ''wp_head'', ''rest_output_link_wp_head'', 10 );\r\nremove_action( ''wp_head'', ''wp_oembed_add_discovery_links'', 10 );</pre><p>将以上代码添加到主题functions.php文件中即可禁用REST API并去除head里面输出的链接信息。</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"http://www.iztwp.com/article/remove-wp-json.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"8";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:17;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:48:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:48:"Healthy Farm 健康/食品/农业等行业主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:44:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/healthy-farm.html";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:52:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/healthy-farm.html#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 10 Dec 2015 05:35:46 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:3:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:12:"高级主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:11:"themeforest";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"自适应";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:34:"http://www.iztwp.com/premium/.html";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:427:"Healthy Farm 是themeforest主题平台上面的一套wordpress主题，这套wordpress主题主要针对健康食品、农业等相关行业设计的，所以页面也采用了非常清新的绿色。主题支持6种首页布局、产品（PORTFOLIO）、博客和商场等功能，支持自适应，以及热门的一些插件（Visual Composer、Revolution Slider等），似的主题功能更加强大。 主题介绍 Mo...";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"爱主题";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4023:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-5596 size-full" src="http://img.iztwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/HealthyFarm.png" alt="Healthy Farm 健康/食品/农业等行业主题" width="590" height="300" /></p>\n<p>Healthy Farm 是<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/go/?r=aHR0cDovL3RoZW1lZm9yZXN0Lm5ldC9jYXRlZ29yeS93b3JkcHJlc3M/cmVmPXdoeXVu" title="themeforest" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">themeforest</a></span>主题平台上面的一套<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/" title="wordpress主题" target="_blank">wordpress主题</a></span>，这套<span class=''wp_keywordlink''><a href="http://www.iztwp.com/" title="wordpress主题" target="_blank">wordpress主题</a></span>主要针对健康食品、农业等相关行业设计的，所以页面也采用了非常清新的绿色。主题支持6种首页布局、产品（PORTFOLIO）、博客和商场等功能，支持自适应，以及热门的一些插件（Visual Composer、Revolution Slider等），似的主题功能更加强大。</p>\n<h3 id="item-description__key-features">主题介绍</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Modern, Flexible, Clean!</li>\n<li>WordPress 4+ Tested and Approved!</li>\n<li>Built with HTML5 and CSS3</li>\n<li>Cross-Browser Compatibility: FireFox, Safari, Chrome, IE9+</li>\n<li>One-Click demo install</li>\n<li>Child theme support</li>\n<li><strong>Layout Features</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>6 Homepage Layouts</li>\n<li>2 Menu Styles</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Multi-Functional User Panel</li>\n<li>2 Footer Styles</li>\n<li>3 Blog Styles</li>\n<li>Fully Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable Retina Option</li>\n<li><strong>Slider Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Includes Revolution Slider</li>\n<li>Post Slider</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Navigation Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>3 Menu Types: Standard Upper Menu, Double Menu, Hide Menu</li>\n<li>Drop-down menu</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Framework</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Setting Inheritance and Override System</li>\n<li>Shortcode Builder</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n<li>Custom Theme Options Panel</li>\n<li>Media Content Manager</li>\n<li>&#8230;and many more!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Translation Options</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Localized: .po &amp; .mo files included</li>\n<li>PO Composer: working with .po and .mo files has now become much easier!</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>Plugins Compatibility</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Revolution Slider</li>\n<li>Visual Composer</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Widgets Set</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Flickr</li>\n<li>Twitter</li>\n<li>Instagram</li>\n<li>Popular Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Posts</li>\n<li>Recent Reviews</li>\n<li>Top 10</li>\n<li>Advertisement</li>\n<li>Logo</li>\n<li>Social Icons</li>\n<li>ThemeRex Shortcodes:</li>\n<li>Blogger</li>\n<li>Content Slider</li>\n<li>Skills</li>\n<li>QR-cod</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>ThemeRex Shortcodes</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Blogger</li>\n<li>Lense</li>\n<li>Content Slider</li>\n<li>Video List</li>\n<li>Skills</li>\n<li>eMailer</li>\n<li>Timeline</li>\n<li>Scroller</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>A lot of <strong>Shortcodes</strong> included:\n<ul>\n<li>Accordion</li>\n<li>Button</li>\n<li>Columns</li>\n<li>Google Map</li>\n<li>Hide</li>\n<li>Highlight</li>\n<li>Section</li>\n<li>Table</li>\n<li>Tabs</li>\n<li>Team</li>\n<li>Testimonials</li>\n<li>Title</li>\n<li>Tooltip</li>\n<li>Toggle</li>\n<li>and more …</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><strong>SEO Ready</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>HTML code integrated into the theme meets the best SEO approaches</li>\n<li>The theme support compatibility with “All on One SEO Pack” &amp; “SEO by Yoast”</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Save money with <strong>Included Plugins</strong>:\n<ul>\n<li>Revolution Slider – $19</li>\n<li>Visual Composer – $30</li>\n<li>PO Composer – $16</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>Performance Optimization</li>\n<li>Two variants of icon display: Fontella Icon set and Images Icons</li>\n<li>Google web fonts</li>\n<li>Great Professional Support</li>\n<li>Documentation included</li>\n<li>Regular Updates</li>\n<li>And many more that we might have forgotten to mention…</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:49:"http://www.iztwp.com/theme/healthy-farm.html/feed";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:3:{s:4:"href";s:25:"http://www.iztwp.com/feed";s:3:"rel";s:4:"self";s:4:"type";s:19:"application/rss+xml";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0